        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5727",
        "content": "This is very cheap.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5727_47030_000012_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5727/47030/5727_47030_000012_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5727",
        "content": "When the rich Sudatta wished to invite the Buddha to a repast, he made use of incense.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5727_47030_000023_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5727/47030/5727_47030_000023_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5727",
        "content": "We shall suppose the game to be arranged for a party of six,-- though there is no rule limiting the number of players.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5727_47030_000023_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5727/47030/5727_47030_000023_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5727",
        "content": "But with the \"guest incense\" no experiment is made.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5727_47030_000024_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5727/47030/5727_47030_000024_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5727",
        "content": "But the faces of the tablets bear numbers or marks; and each set comprises three tablets numbered \"one,\" three numbered \"two,\" three numbered \"three,\" and one marked with the character signifying \"guest.\" After these tablet sets have been distributed, a box called the \"tablet box\" is placed before the first player; and all is ready for the real game.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5727_47030_000025_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5727/47030/5727_47030_000025_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5727",
        "content": "He takes the six tablets out of the box, and wraps them up in the paper which contained the incense guessed about.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5727_47030_000027_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5727/47030/5727_47030_000027_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5727",
        "content": "But it is quite a feat to make ten correct judgments in succession.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5727_47030_000027_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5727/47030/5727_47030_000027_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5727",
        "content": "The olfactory nerves are apt to become somewhat numbed long before the game is concluded; and, therefore it is customary during the Ko kwai to rinse the mouth at intervals with pure vinegar, by which operation the sensitivity is partially restored.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5727_47030_000028_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5727/47030/5727_47030_000028_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5727",
        "content": "RECORD OF A KO KWAI.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5727_47030_000038_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5727/47030/5727_47030_000038_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5727",
        "content": "It is the custom In some families to enter all such records in a book especially made for the purpose, and furnished with an index which enables the Ko kwai player to refer immediately to any interesting fact belonging to the history of any past game.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5727_47030_000042_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5727/47030/5727_47030_000042_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5727",
        "content": "To twenty one pastilles",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5727_47030_000043_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5727/47030/5727_47030_000043_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5727",
        "content": "Recipe for Baikwa.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5727_47030_000047_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5727/47030/5727_47030_000047_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5727",
        "content": "Finally I may observe that, while judging the incense, a player is expected to take not less than three inhalations, or more than five.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5727_47030_000048_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5727/47030/5727_47030_000048_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5727",
        "content": "In this economical era, the Ko kwai takes of necessity a much humbler form than it assumed in the time of the great daimyo, of the princely abbots, and of the military aristocracy.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5727_47030_000048_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5727/47030/5727_47030_000048_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5727",
        "content": "A full set of the utensils required for the game can now be had for about fifty dollars; but the materials are of the poorest kind.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5727_47030_000055_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5727/47030/5727_47030_000055_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5727",
        "content": "When the Emperor had lost his beautiful favorite, the Lady Li, he sorrowed so much that fears were entertained for his reason.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5727_47030_000057_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5727/47030/5727_47030_000057_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5727",
        "content": "Although the power of making visible the forms of the dead has been claimed for one sort of incense only, the burning of any kind of incense is supposed to summon viewless spirits in multitude.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5727_47032_000004_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5727/47032/5727_47032_000004_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5727",
        "content": "\"Is it possible,\" he exclaimed, \"that you never saw a silkworm moth?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5727_47032_000004_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5727/47032/5727_47032_000004_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5727",
        "content": "The silkworm moth has very beautiful eyebrows.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5727_47032_000005_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5727/47032/5727_47032_000005_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5727",
        "content": "\"Well, call them what you like,\" returned Niimi;--\"the poets call them eyebrows....",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5727_47032_000006_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5727/47032/5727_47032_000006_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5727",
        "content": "He left the guest room, and presently returned with a white paper fan, on which a silkworm moth was sleepily reposing.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5727_47032_000007_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5727/47032/5727_47032_000007_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5727",
        "content": "It cannot fly, of course: none of them can fly....",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5727_47032_000007_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5727/47032/5727_47032_000007_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5727",
        "content": "Now look at the eyebrows.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5727_47032_000009_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5727/47032/5727_47032_000009_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5727",
        "content": "Then Niimi took me to see his worms.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5727_47032_000010_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5727/47032/5727_47032_000010_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5727",
        "content": "As they approach maturity, the creatures need almost constant attention.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5727_47032_000010_000008",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5727/47032/5727_47032_000010_000008.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5727",
        "content": "They have mouths, but do not eat.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5727_47032_000010_000009",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5727/47032/5727_47032_000010_000009.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5727",
        "content": "They only pair, lay eggs, and die.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5727_47032_000016_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5727/47032/5727_47032_000016_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5727",
        "content": "Those silkworms have all that they wish for,--even considerably more.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5727_47032_000017_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5727/47032/5727_47032_000017_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5727",
        "content": "Let pain and its effort be suspended, and life must shrink back, first into protoplasmic shapelessness, thereafter into dust.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5727_47032_000019_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5727/47032/5727_47032_000019_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5727",
        "content": "In a silkworm paradise such as our mundane instincts lead us to desire, the seraph freed from the necessity of toil, and able to satisfy his every want at will, would lose his wings at last, and sink back to the condition of a grub....",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
